## рҹ“Ң Features

* вң… User Signup & Login (JWT аӨҶаӨ§аӨҫаӨ°аӨҝаӨӨ authentication)
* рҹ”җ Protected Routes (only logged-in users can access tasks)
* рҹ“қ Add Tasks
* вңҸпёҸ Edit Tasks
* вқҢ Delete Tasks
* вң”пёҸ Mark Tasks as Completed
* рҹ”Қ Search Tasks
* рҹ“Ӯ Categories (Work, Personal, Urgent)
* рҹҡӘ Logout System

